What you need to know:

Tuchel, whose axing was widely reported but unconfirmed last week, managed PSG 127 times in all competitions, with 95 wins, 12 draws and 20 defeatsArgentinian Mauricio Pochettino is widely reported to be the favourite to become the next PSG coachThe 47-year-old German also led the Parisian club to their first ever Champions League final last August, which they lost 1-0 to Bayern Munich